'''Nadege Uwamwezi''' (wavutse 1993), ni umukinnyi wa filimi mu  [[Rwanda]] . Umwe mu bakinnyi ba filime bazwi cyane muri filimi zo kuri televiziyo  mu [[Rwanda]], Nadege azwi cyane ku ruhare 'Nana' mu biganiro bya televiziyo, ''City Maid'' .  Usibye gukina, ni n'umuririmbyi n'munyamideri.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1993 mu Rwanda.

Yafunguye butike yitwa 'Nana Fashion Shop' ifite izina rye.  Afite umuhungu umwe kuva yashyingiranwa bwa mbere, Ganza Benny Lucky. 

Nkâ€™uko ibihuha bivugwa, ngo yaba akundana n'umuririmbyi [[Kizito Mihigo]] . Ariko nyuma yaje kubihakana, avuga ko ari inshuti gusa. Icyakora, vuba aha byavuzwe ko bategura ubukwe. Icyakora, yongeye guhakana ibyo aregwa. 

== Umwuga ==
Mbere yo gukina, Nadege yari umuririmbyi waririmbye ku izina rya 'Umwamikazi Nadege'. Yari mu itsinda ryitwa 'The Queens' aho baririmbaga 'Ryajambo' mu 2009. 

Yinjiye muri Kwetu Film Institute yiga ikinamico. Nyuma, yamenyekanye gukina na Kennedy Mazimpaka, amaze kubona ubuhanga bwe bwo gukina i Kwetu. Mazimpaka yamuhaye uruhare ruto muri filime ''Rwasibo'', yaje kuba umukinnyi wa mbere wa sinema.  Mu mwaka wa 2016, yakinnye muri filimi ica kuri televiziyo ''Mutoni'' nk'uruhare rwo kuyobora. 

Nyuma, yakinnye muri firime nyinshi zizwi cyane na  zirimo, ''Catherine'' na ''Nkubito ya Nyamunsi'' . Muri 2016, yakinnye muri ''City Maid'' . filimi imaze kumenyekana cyane mubantu kandi yakundaga kwitwa 'Nana'. 

